title: #58: Stuntman (Tait Fletcher)
itunes:title: Stuntman with Tait Fletcher
description: Tait Fletcher stopped by my hovel to talk to me about stunt work. Tait works as a full stuntman for TV and movies. We meandered into talk about Bruce Lee, Master P and how horrible actresses are.
